Misol

“Banan” so‘zining 20 ta belgidan iborat, chapga asoslangan versiyasini qaytaring:

txt = "banana"

x = txt.ljust(20)

print(x, "is my favorite fruit.")

Eslatma: Natijada, banan so'zining o'ng tomonida 14 ta bo'sh joy mavjud.

Ta'rifi va qo'llanilishi
Usul ljust()to'ldirish belgisi sifatida belgilangan belgidan (bo'sh joy sukut bo'yicha) foydalanib, satrni chapga tekislaydi.

Sintaksis
string.ljust(length, character)

Parametr qiymatlari
Parameter	Description
length ----	Required. The length of the returned string
character ----	Optional. A character to fill the missing space (to the right of the string). Default is " " (space).

Misol
To'ldirish belgisi sifatida "O" harfidan foydalanish:

txt = "banana"

x = txt.ljust(20, "O")

print(x)
